content: I am proficient in both English and Swedish, and am looking for work relating to translating papers from English to Swedish and vice versa.*Pay rate: currently at $0.05 per word*Free samples: if you're a trusted member of Bitcointalk with at least the rank of Senior Member, I'm willing to do a free sample for you, post on this thread if you're interested.If anyone is interested, feel free to post here, or PM me
